Package MusicBrainz

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    SearchOnlineDatabase
    The Target in the Adapter pattern that allows the adapter to change the style of the request into a query for music brainz
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Artist
    Artist Object Created from MusicBrainz gson
    ArtistCredit
    This class represents the artist who created the song and then the artist object that goes with that name
    MusicBrainz
    MusicBrainz class is the class that will make the query to the online database, it wil then pass that response from the query to the MusicBrainzJson class
    MusicBrainzAdapter
    This class will change the args into a query string that the Music Brainz Class ccn use to find the info for the query needs to be passed in from the Search Request
    MusicBrainzJson
    This Class will take the response from the MusixBrainz Query and turn them into a List of real objects
    Release
    A release object that is created from the music Brainz Object
    ReleaseList
    This is a list of release objects created from the gson
    Song
    This Class represents a Song object in the MusicBrainz Database
    SongList
    SongList is a list of songs created from the query parsed through from gson
